{
  "stem": "9.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Very little meat-- I mean, meat was unheard of whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, potatoes, and vegetables, and maybe some fruit in the season was available.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, I do want to bring up that there was a tremendous traffic in the sewer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My husband was one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He belonged to a underground, and their job was to buy ammunition on the outside-- not food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was another group that dealt with food-- [LAUGHS] and bring it into the ghetto for protection.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To tell you how bad it was-- my husband, who was in the army when the war broke out-- and he was one of the first few being caught into one of the camps.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went into Majdenek-- M-A-J-D-E-N-E-K.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He did accomplish, because it was in the beginning of the war, to get some papers from the governor-- and with bribing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he had a lot of gold and diamonds, because his job in the camp was to unpack the suitcases that the people brought before they went in to being killed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not sure there was a gas chamber yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had an awful lot of gold and diamonds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he didn't know what to do with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he managed to bribe a Ukrainian guard and a Latvian guard-- and they were the worst.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And his whole bribe was that they deliver a letter to a governor-- well, first, to his girlfriend, and then a governor in turn.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he got an official permission to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because he was working for the governor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he came home to his own parents when the whole family was intact, and told them that times are-- bad times are coming.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Leave the place-- run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody believed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't get attached to possessions.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
